      <title>贝莱德斥资 125 亿美元收购基础设施公司 GIP，推动替代方案的重大发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/blackrock-buys-infrastructure-firm-gip-for-12-5-billion-in-alternatives-push</link>
